## Summary
The Amplitude Experiment Ruby SDK documentation covers both remote and local evaluation methods for feature flags, including initialization, configuration, fetching variants, and evaluating users, with support for cohort targeting, automatic assignment tracking, and integration with Amplitude cookies.

